### Login as Admin (Default credentials)
POST http://localhost:5016/api/users/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@salesapp.com",
  "password": "admin123"
}

### Register New User (Admin only - use token from login)
POST http://localhost:5016/api/users/register
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "John Doe",
  "email": "john@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "role": "normal"
}

### Get All Users (Admin only)
GET http://localhost:5016/api/users?page=1&pageSize=10&search=
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Get User by ID (Admin or self)
GET http://localhost:5016/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### Update User (Admin or self)
PUT http://localhost:5016/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

{
  "name": "John Updated",
  "email": "john.updated@example.com"
}

### Delete User (Admin only - soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:5016/api/users/USER_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE